This paper is about natural language processing and specifically focuses on training language models using recurrent neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses optimization algorithms and model architecture, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions using context such as images, which suggests computer vision (cs.CV) may also be relevant. Finally, the paper discusses the speed of the proposed method, which could be relevant to neural networks (cs.NE).
